This is clone of the mpiP repository from Sourceforge.

* Contains MM specific changes to add printing of Rank specific MPI Time data.
* Also contains MM specific Point to Point profiling of "Bytes" and "MPI Time"
  between pairs of source and destination ranks.

How to Deploy this repository ?

* Clone this repository within the perftools directory structure.

git clone https://rahulsaxena@bitbucket.org/rahulsaxena/mpip.git

* perftools$> make install-mpip

* To Enable Rank Specific MPI Time information and to enable 
  Rank to Rank Bytes and MPI Time details use the '-q' option to the MPIP env variable